description: Welcom to Google Analyzer Application 1st pilot: To run the application you need the following: 1- Download Node.js JavaScript runtime from : https://nodejs.org/en/  2- Download this projact to your directory 3- cd into the directory and type npm install --save  and npm install --save google-trends-api. 4- Use npm init to save these settings.
